{
  "stem": "18670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other thing is there were days you got hungry, so we developed a way of stilling our hunger.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would take a piece of bread and go in front of a delicatessen store, break the bread in half and get the whiff coming out, so when you had a bag of bread, the other bread was the hot dog or the hamburger or whatever it was, a piece of corned beef, whatever smelled good, a chicken, a roast chicken.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this is how we used to fill our stomach, take a bite of bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And occasionally we spent some money on ice cream.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had delicious ice cream-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You asked me before whether we brought any clothing across.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, I think it was, had a distant cousin, a diamond dealer in Brussel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got his name and address.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they sent us two suitcases, one for my brother, one for me, to this cousin, distant cousin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember like the day we went up there and he says, you're going to America?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They don't speak any Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're going to be lost.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had been to America before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They don't talk Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, you're going to be lost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, we got the suitcases, so we had some thing, a few things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had a change.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a suit to wear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They mailed us some money, not too much, because there were limitations how much money you could send out, right?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got some money, not a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did a little business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was such a thing to get around those controls, I would buy international stamps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And actually no, it was this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
